      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring a blueprinted S54 inline-six engine with meticulously synchronized individual throttle bodies and a refreshed double VANOS system. The chassis integrity is absolute, having undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a complete suspension overhaul with high-durometer bushings to preserve the factory-spec kinematics. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution and corner-exit traction. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero evidence of clear coat failure or panel misalignment, while the cabin features pristine upholstery and fully functional, tactile switchgear. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example of Bavarian performance.",
